  "instructions": [
    "Heat the melted coconut oil in a Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the pear and cook until slightly caramelized.",
    "Add the gluten-free pan-canton noodles and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the full-fat coconut milk and stir to coat the noodles.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the homemade or store-bought beurre-monte sauce.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Simmer for an additional 2 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
